{"id":"errors/NG01003","title":"NG01003: Async validator must return a Promise or Observable\n\n非同步驗證器必須返回一個 Promise 或 Observable","contents":"<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/errors/NG01003.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng01003-async-validator-must-return-a-promise-or-observable非同步驗證器必須返回一個-promise-或-observable\">NG01003: Async validator must return a Promise or Observable\n\n非同步驗證器必須返回一個 Promise 或 Observable<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG01003#ng01003-async-validator-must-return-a-promise-or-observable非同步驗證器必須返回一個-promise-或-observable\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  \n  \n\n  <div class=\"error-description\">\n    <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"說明\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG01003#說明\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG01003#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">非同步驗證器必須返回 promise 或 observable，並且無論驗證失敗還是成功都會發出/解析它們。特別是，它們必須實現<a href=\"api/forms/AsyncValidator\">AsyncValidatorFn API</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Async validators must return a promise or an observable, and emit/resolve them whether the validation fails or succeeds. In particular, they must implement the <a href=\"api/forms/AsyncValidator\">AsyncValidatorFn API</a></p>\n\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nexport function isTenAsync(control: <a href=\"api/forms/AbstractControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">AbstractControl</a>): \n  Observable&lt;<a href=\"api/forms/ValidationErrors\" class=\"code-anchor\">ValidationErrors</a> | null&gt; {\n    const v: number = control.value;\n    if (v !== 10) {\n    // Emit an object with a validation error.\n      return of({ 'notTen': true, 'requiredValue': 10 });\n    }\n    // Emit null, to indicate no error occurred.\n    return of(null);\n  }\n</code-example>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <br>\n\n  <div class=\"debugging\">\n    <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"如何排除本錯誤\">如何排除本錯誤<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG01003#如何排除本錯誤\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"debugging-the-error\">Debugging the error<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG01003#debugging-the-error\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">你是否錯誤地使用了同步驗證器而不是非同步驗證器？</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Did you mistakenly use a synchronous validator instead of an async validator?</p>\n\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - errors\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/forms/AbstractControl\n - api/forms/AsyncValidator\n - api/forms/ValidationErrors\n - errors/NG01003#debugging-the-error\n - errors/NG01003#description\n - errors/NG01003#ng01003-async-validator-must-return-a-promise-or-observable非同步驗證器必須返回一個-promise-或-observable\n - errors/NG01003#如何排除本錯誤\n - errors/NG01003#說明\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/errors/NG01003.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}